#Sum of n even numbers:-
n=int(input('enter n value:'))
sum=0
for i in range (1,n+1):
    if i%2==0:
      sum=sum+i
      print(sum)
      
print('sum of even numbers:',sum)

OUTPUT:-
enter n value:
20
2
6
12
20
30
42
56
72
90
110
sum of even numbers: 110


